  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a vampire-skuf who lives in a castle, loves collecting figurines, and spends his days at the computer. But it’s not all chill — adventurers constantly try to raid the castle in search of treasure. You’ll need to summon collectible monsters, build new rooms, and defend your lair... but hey, the match won’t play itself, and the world can wait. ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685120/extras/347d3a00c0cd11eae8cddcda4077d11e.avif?t=1763784545\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685120/extras_big/347d3a00c0cd11eae8cddcda4077d11e.avif?t=1763784545 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampire vibes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect creatures — Unlock figurines to summon matching monsters! Level them up and place them in rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How many memes are in the game? — YES.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character — A vampire-skuf</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685120/extras/66c9fe2db06eb24de9dc5ac31a7271a4.avif?t=1763784545\" width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a vampire-skuf who lives in a castle, loves collecting figurines, and spends his days at the computer. But it’s not all chill — adventurers constantly try to raid the castle in search of treasure. You’ll need to summon collectible monsters, build new rooms, and defend your lair... but hey, the match won’t play itself, and the world can wait. ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685120/extras/347d3a00c0cd11eae8cddcda4077d11e.avif?t=1763784545\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685120/extras_big/347d3a00c0cd11eae8cddcda4077d11e.avif?t=1763784545 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampire vibes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect creatures — Unlock figurines to summon matching monsters! Level them up and place them in rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How many memes are in the game? — YES.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character — A vampire-skuf</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3685120/extras/66c9fe2db06eb24de9dc5ac31a7271a4.avif?t=1763784545\" width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li></ul>",
